@returns {number} The error function integrated between lower_limit and upper_limit
@see For further information, see {@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#ERF | docs.oasis-open.org}
