@returns {number} the number of permutations for a given number of objects (with repetitions) that can be selected from the total objects or an error if the arguments are incorrect.
@see For further information, see {@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#PERMUTATIONA | docs.oasis-open.org}

=PHI.!doc:
