@see For further information, see {@link https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/office/quartile-inc-function-1bbacc80-5075-42f1-aed6-47d735c4819d | support.microsoft.com}

=QUOTIENT.!doc:
@category:Math & Trigonometry
Returns the integer portion of a division.

@param {number} numerator Number that is the dividend.
@param {number} denominator Number that is the divisor.
@returns {number} The quotient of the two arguments (integer portion).
@see For futher information, see&nbsp;{@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#QUOTIENT | docs.oasis-open.org}
